4. Cost telemetry / token burn rate per dispatch
5. Cross-skill dependency graph
6. Mobile-eats end-user health
7. Operator fatigue gate
8. Cross-time synthesis
9. Adversarial/red-team orchestrator self-audit
10. Public artifact pipeline

Add these fields to the tick receipt:
