At tick close, after dispatch/refill decisions and before returning control to
the loop driver, run the AGENTS.md fleet propagation probe in dry-run mode:

```bash
/Users/josh/Developer/flywheel/.flywheel/scripts/agents-md-fleet-propagator.sh \
